{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回\"冒牌大盗的亡命窝\"中，陆小凤与金七两在荒漠春色中相遇。金七两透露自己为追捕蛇郎君来到此地，却发现沙大户收留的亡命客全是冒牌货，令陆小凤追查柳乘风凶手的线索中断。金七两介绍镇上唯一非本地人的宫素素——一位因犯事被放逐的王爷爱妃，引发陆小凤的好奇。本章通过两人对话揭示了沙大户爱面子却收留假大盗的荒诞，以及宫素素神秘的身世背景。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆小鸟。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "其实我不该叫你陆小鸟的，你看起来根本不像一只鸟。你看起来，简直就像只小鸡。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "金七两，你来干什么？是不是来追我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我要追，至少也要追一只母鸡，来追你这只小公鸡干什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我是没法子，是被逼得非跑出来不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "谁逼你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "人逼不走我，只有气才逼得走我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "谁的气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然是大老板的气。也只有大老板的气才能逼人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "大老板在生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不但在生气，而且气得要命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "他在生谁的气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "当然是在生你的气。他早就已经关照厨房，把酒菜准备好，你却死也不肯留下来吃饭，如果你是他，你气不气？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "我不气。非但不气，而且还开心得要命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "开心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "我没有留在他那里吃饭，他的酒也省了一点，菜也省了一点，为什么不开心？为什么要生气？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "大概就因为你不是他，所以才会说这种话，我们这位大老板是个死要面子的人，陆小凤既然已经来到他的地盘，居然不肯在他家里吃一顿饭，这对他说来，简直是奇耻大辱，简直比偷了他老婆还要让他生气，所以这顿饭我也吃不下去了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "所以你就只好偷偷的溜出来找我？你是不是想要我请大吃一顿？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "本来是我想请你的，可是如果你一定要请我，我也不会太不给你面子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "本来我是真的想请你的，只可惜这里连个饭馆都没有，我就算想请你也没有法子请。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "有办法，只要你肯花钱，我就有办法，如果连别人的钱我都花不出去，我就不是金七两，而是金土狗了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到老板娘居然有这么好的手艺。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这不是老板娘的手艺，是王老板的手艺。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "而且他好像什么都吃。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "别人在他店里，偷他一个鸡蛋他都看得清清楚楚，偷他老婆他却看不见。你知不知道这个镇上有一句很流行的俏皮话？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "赵瞎子有一双什么都能看得见的贼眼，王大眼却是个睁眼瞎子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆小凤，我老实告诉你，我们见面的次数虽然不多，可是我一直把你当作我的朋友。就算你不把我当朋友，我也要把你当朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你一定觉得很奇怪，奇怪我为什么会逃亡到这里来。天下之大，我金七两什么地方不可以去，什么地方没有把我当贵宾一样看待的大阔佬？我为什么要到这里来投奔那个狂妄自大、死要面子的活土狗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "那么你为什么要到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为了一条蛇，一条比赤练蛇还要毒一百倍的毒蛇。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "你说的这条蛇，大概不是一条蛇，而是一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "你说的这个人，大概就是蛇郎君。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这个人不但比蛇还毒，而且比蛇还滑，我盯他已经盯了七八个月，直到最近才听人说他在这条路上出现过。我也听说这地方有位沙大老板，只要是在江湖上有点名头的朋友，只要到这里来了，不管他身上背着多大的案子，沙大老板都一概收留。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "所以你就认定那条蛇一定在沙大户那里避仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "无论谁都会这么想的。你大概也会认为，你要找的那一男一女，一定都是沙大老板收留的亡命客。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是你错了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "你怎么知道我错了，你怎么知道我要找的人不在那些亡命客之中？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他们都认为我真的杀了小小田，都认为田八太爷非要我的命不可，所以什么事都不避我。他们已经把我看成他们的同类，谁也没想到那只不过是个幌子而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "沙大老板总是喜欢很神秘的告诉别人，他家里窝藏着多少个亡命江湖的大盗，偶尔还会假装不小心的透露出几个名字来。他说出来的名字，的确都是轰动过一时的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "能够把几个声名赫赫的江洋大盗，窝藏在家里，倒真的是件很过瘾的事。不但他自己觉得过瘾，别人也会觉得他很有面子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "大老板都是要面子的，只不过这位沙大老板要得太过分了一点。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "怎么样过分？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他要面子，已经要得快要没有面子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为他窝藏的那些大名鼎鼎的巨盗，全都是冒牌货。这些人知道大老板的脾气，所以就投其所好，有的自称为横行江淮间的某某某，有的打着杀人如麻的某某某的旗号。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "其实呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "其实他们全都只不过是些下三流的小贼而已，非但没有蛇郎君那一号的人物，连个像样的角都没有。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "在这一群胡说八道混吃混喝的小王八蛋里面，怎么会有你要找的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "陆小鸟，你用不着难过，要难过，我比你更难过。看来我们都一样，这一次都白跑了一趟，不如一起打道回府吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "这地方这么好玩，我怎么舍得走！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说这地方好玩？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "当然好玩。好玩极了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "除了那一批冒牌大盗之外，别的人难道全都是土生土长在这里的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好像是的。好像只有一个人不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "谁？谁不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "宫素素。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "她是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她是个女人，风度非常好，学识也非常好，见解很独特，谈吐也很优雅，而且琴棋书画无一不精。她只有一点不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "她喜欢喝酒。有一次我亲眼看见她一顿饭喝了一坛莲花白，喝完了之后，面不改色。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果你要问我，像这么样一个人，怎么能在这种地方待得下去？那么我告诉你，她并不是自己要到这里来的，而是想走却走不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为她本来是当朝一位亲贵王爷的爱妃，因为犯事坐罪，触怒了王爷，才被放逐到这里来的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "我知道，我知道你是在害我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我在害你？我怎么会害你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "text": "你明明晓得我听到这个地方有这么样一个女人，如果不见她一面，连觉也睡不着的。现在你叫我怎么办？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_qi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "金七两",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "怎么办？好办极了。你要见她，我就带你去，而且还要叫她请你喝酒。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    }
